Original:
外國人在這裡說這是我去過的最友好的酒吧之一，特別是與我在美國習慣的酒吧相比。工作人員對他們的飲料非常了解（甚至向我介紹了他們的威士忌選擇，我在這個過程中收到了極好的推薦）。

有些工作人員會說英語，但他們都盡力讓我感到賓至如歸。在交通緩慢的時候，這裡是遠離外面暴風雨的綠洲，而在繁忙的時候，這個地方才真正變得生氣勃勃。工作人員也會努力讓您保持充足的水分，並且談話總是真誠而有趣。考慮到酒吧的選擇、服務品質和清潔度，飲料的價格相當合理。

每個酒吧都應該努力實現這家酒吧所體現的目標。

中仁
EN:
Foreigners said here that this is one of the most friendly bars I have been, especially compared with the bars I used to in the United States.The staff knows very much about their drinks (even introducing me to their whiskey choices, and I received excellent recommendations in the process).

Some staff members speak English, but they try their best to make me feel as expensive.When the traffic is slow, this is the oasis away from the storm outside the outside, and at the busy time, this place really becomes angry.The staff will also work hard to keep you sufficient water, and the conversation is always sincere and interesting.Considering the selection, service quality and cleanliness of the bar, the price of beverages is quite reasonable.

Each bar should work hard to achieve the goals reflected in this bar.

Medium benevolence
